WEBVTT

00:09:57.195 --> 00:10:00.892
Kama mgonjwa huyo ana mtu
katika dunia ya nje

00:10:00.916 --> 00:10:02.829
wa kuwaongoza na kuwasaidia,

00:10:02.853 --> 00:10:07.217
daktari anaweza pendekeza matunzo bora
akiwa na uelewa na yale mahusiano akilini.

00:10:08.075 --> 00:10:11.261
Katika utabibu, watu
wanaunganika kama wanadamu

00:10:11.285 --> 00:10:14.517
kabla hawajatambulika
kama daktari na mgonjwa.

00:10:15.699 --> 00:10:18.254
Lakini njia hii ya kuongeza utambuzi --

00:10:18.278 --> 00:10:19.756
haitakiwi kuwa haribifu,

00:10:19.780 --> 00:10:22.580
na haina mahitaji ya kukarabati
namna ya kutazama.

